title: Looking for team members! Must be D5 or better! ADC/TOP/SUP/JUN Tryouts ASAP
body:
Current team is falling apart. I'm currently D2, Highest i've ever been was Chal #2. Competent shot-caller.  Looking for players who are friendly, but believe they can go even with top tier players. We are an organization, so i'm not a solo man making a team.
Write here before adding me in-game(iG Cohen).
Thanks!
